{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Complete removal of VAT for companies based in UK.",
        "additional_details": "Complete removal of VAT from \r\n1.\tall products designed manufactured and sold in UK.\r\n2.\tall services offered by UK companies in UK and abroad.\r\n3.\tVAT free sales to any company with local HQ.\r\n\r\nNo exceptions of product service or company as long as of UK origin or HQ based in UK. \r\n\r\nWithin 2 years, or the time for Brexit to take effect.\r\n\r\nAll VAT collections should be used to pay the Brexit bill of \u00a340bn.\r\n\r\nIt's citizens money, let citizens keep it and spend it as they find convenient.",
        "background": "VAT is a protectionist device of German and French origin. It was adopted by the EU starting at certain rates, that it has almost doubled without explanation. It particularly burdens lower classes and offers tax loopholes to the rich who can set camp in VAT free places.",
